      <!-- FAQ Page -->
      <div class="page page-faq" style="display:none;">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="help-card">
          <h4>Do I need to register?</h4>
          <p>No registration is required. Just configure your miner with your wallet address and start mining!</p>

          <h4>What is PPLNS?</h4>
          <p>PPLNS stands for "Pay Per Last N Shares". This reward system pays miners based on the last N shares contributed when a block is found. It rewards loyal miners and discourages pool hopping.</p>

          <h4>When do I get paid?</h4>
          <p>Payments are processed automatically when your balance reaches the minimum payout threshold. Check the pool configuration for specific amounts.</p>

          <h4>How accurate is the hashrate display?</h4>
          <p>The hashrate is calculated based on submitted shares. Short-term fluctuations are normal. The 3-hour average provides the most accurate representation.</p>

          <h4>What if my worker shows as offline?</h4>
          <p>Workers are marked offline if no shares are submitted for 15 minutes. Check your miner configuration and network connection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Support Page -->
      <div class="page page-support" style="display:none;">
        <h2>Support</h2>

        <div style="background-color: var(--card-bg); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; box-shadow: var(--shadow);">
          <i class="fab fa-discord" style="font-size: 48px; color: var(--accent-primary); margin-bottom: 20px;"></i>
          <h3>Join Our Community</h3>
          <p style="margin: 20px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">Get help, share tips, and connect with other miners!</p>
          <a href="https://discord.gg/ZyG3YKDCQQ" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fab fa-discord"></i> Join Discord
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Help Page -->
      <div class="page page-help" style="display:none;">
        <div class="help-content">
          <h2>Getting Started Guide</h2>

          <div class="help-card">
            <h3>Quick Start</h3>
            <p>Follow these simple steps to start mining:</p>

            <h4>1. Choose Your Coin</h4>
            <p>Select a coin from the home page based on your hardware and preferences.</p>

            <h4>2. Get a Wallet</h4>
            <p>Download the official wallet for your chosen coin and generate a receiving address.</p>

            <h4>3. Download Mining Software</h4>
            <p>Choose compatible mining software for your hardware:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>GPU Mining:</strong> T-Rex, NBMiner, TeamRedMiner</li>
              <li><strong>CPU Mining:</strong> XMRig, CPUminer</li>
              <li><strong>ASIC Mining:</strong> Check manufacturer's software</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>4. Configure Your Miner</h4>
            <p>Use the configuration examples from the Connect page for your specific setup.</p>

            <div class="command-box">
              miner.exe -a ALGORITHM -o stratum+tcp://POOL:PORT -u WALLET.WORKER
            </div>

            <h4>5. Monitor Your Stats</h4>
